name: Old Entity Hastorr
effectText:
1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters
If this card is sent from the Monster Zone to the GY: You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; equip this card from your GY to that monster. That monster cannot attack, also its effects are negated. If this card leaves the field while equipped to an opponent's monster by this effect: Take control of the monster this card was equipped to.
